      • shortSignedAtOffset

        private static java.lang.Integer shortSignedAtOffset(byte[] c,
                                                     int offset)
        Gyroscope, Magnetometer, Barometer, IR temperature all store 16 bit two's complement values as LSB MSB, which cannot be directly parsed as getIntValue(FORMAT_SINT16, offset) because the bytes are stored as little-endian. This function extracts these 16 bit two's complement values.
        Parameters:
        c - some byte
        offset - some offset
